{"tid":2374926,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂46討論區#461：新内眞衣 & 生田絵梨花お誕生日おめでとう！","createTime":"2021-01-21T14:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T15:01:48.000Z","uid":19698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d96ea191240937d71954054da78ee36cc2e3609","tid":2374926,"uid":19698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:59:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span class=\"red\"><p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\">新内眞衣 &amp; 生田絵梨花 お誕生日おめでとう！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BAENCsh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBAENCsh.jpg&h=0621c51e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6sjNCsh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6sjNCsh.jpg&h=f862e5ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NucLo7h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNucLo7h.jpg&h=926ba506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wN6HrkC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwN6HrkC.jpg&h=8170d4da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></p></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/of84uck.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fof84uck.jpg&h=5378bdb0&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<span class=\"red\">乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一至四期生在內，團體目前共有48名成員，而隊長為秋元真夏。其與2015年8月21日成立的櫸坂46、以及2019年2月11日自櫸坂46獨立的日向坂46，構成大型偶像組合系列「坂道系列」。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團名取自坐落東京都赤坂地區乃木坂的「SME乃木坂大樓」，該建築為所屬唱片公司日本索尼音樂的前辦公大樓之一。根據秋元康所說，<span class=\"red\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"purple\"><p class=\"center\">-NEWS-</p></span><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><p class=\"center\"><br />\n26thシングル『僕は僕を好きになる』<br />\n<span class=\"red\">1月27日発売</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRBQ9mo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRBQ9mo.jpg&h=326b8e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F_WgREJgJhw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DF_WgREJgJhw&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcJ4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=7180ee6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F_WgREJgJhw</a><br />\n<br />\n鈴木絢音1st写真集『光の角度』<br />\n<span class=\"red\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.gentosha.jp/files/uploads/content/202010/images/img_nx0s2NeztT0wTwWGcZGDgikgtGFg38XCUPhK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gentosha.jp%2Ffiles%2Fuploads%2Fcontent%2F202010%2Fimages%2Fimg_nx0s2NeztT0wTwWGcZGDgikgtGFg38XCUPhK.jpg&h=a275496d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白石麻衣 乃木坂46卒業記念メモリアルマガジン<br />\n<span class=\"red\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHCnCi1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHCnCi1.jpg&h=4c25a4ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMusic Video集「ALL MV COLLECTION２～あの時の彼女たち～」<br />\n<span class=\"red\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vVnMD8R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVnMD8R.jpg&h=27787ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"></span></p><p class=\"center\"><br />\n乃木坂46 配信限定曲『Route 246』<br />\n<span class=\"red\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCoH77V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCoH77V.jpg&h=6e68d9c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中田花奈1st写真集<br />\n<span class=\"red\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S46Lz32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS46Lz32.jpg&h=df6d78ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梅澤美波1st写真集『夢の近く』<br />\n<span class=\"red\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://actresspress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1957975392d55b468f43956447ce3587-scaled.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Factresspress.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F1957975392d55b468f43956447ce3587-scaled.jpg&h=bb76d3aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n与田祐希 2nd写真集『無口な時間』<br />\n<span class=\"red\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbnail.image.rakuten.co.jp/@0_mall/book/cabinet/9619/2100011829619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbnail.image.rakuten.co.jp%2F%400_mall%2Fbook%2Fcabinet%2F9619%2F2100011829619.jpg&h=f3c7875e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n秋元真夏2nd写真集『しあわせにしたい』<br />\n<span class=\"red\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E09mMtJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE09mMtJ.jpg&h=fb4bd72d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堀未央奈2nd写真集『いつかの待ち合わせ場所』<br />\n<span class=\"red\">発売中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kCZaTy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kCZaTy.jpg&h=90f8cb08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p></span><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\">乃木坂46成員列表（最新）</span></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiwFp7s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiwFp7s.jpg&h=a613c338&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEdDWed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEdDWed.jpg&h=2ee64564&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wOdMkF0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOdMkF0.jpg&h=772b3c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WnYbNH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WnYbNH.jpg&h=89f903c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SYFCsk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSYFCsk5.jpg&h=1e5a7602&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><a href=\"http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/nogizaka46sort.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkeyakizaka46style.com%2Fsort%2Fnogizaka46sort.html&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcJ4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=441d1c82\" target=\"_blank\">http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/nogizaka46sort.html</a></p><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\">請新/舊手足定期體檢</span></p><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><p class=\"center\">Q&amp;A</p></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...不如幫襯某良心代購小店，詳情請向手足查詢。另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員，但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n<del>直接飛去日本或中國參加握手會、演唱會、見面會，但不要幻想會再來港，因香港已經柒出國際。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。</del> <br />\n<del>Online Meet</del> 無<br />\n<br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦？<br />\n無<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f96542f8480a1a34e14c14092c7c8650a7028e0f","tid":2374926,"uid":284779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"花花&amp;OL<br />\n<br />\n生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee79ab8e03c105ddcff8a8f767a91f24e1d3701","tid":2374926,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"樓主會開過個po，勿推"}]}